  "text": "The measurement model defines the latent variables that are used and assigns manifest variables (indicators) to each one. The evaluation of the measurement model for the reflective indicators in PLS is based on the reliability of each item, the reliability of the construct (CR), the convergent validity and the discriminant validity [CITATION_1] ).",
